<h2>01. Bridge to Erikson Springs Campground </h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>V+ (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>11 Miles </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-3'>
<th>Avg. Gradient</th>
<td>189 fpm</td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-4'>
<th>Max Gradient</th>
<td>385 fpm</td>
</tr>
</table>
