<br>
<h2>River Description</h2>
Remote, woody, manky, scenic, epic, hard on the plastic. Check out the article on Ruby by Evan J.
Stafford at <a href="http://www.coloradokayaking.com/main.php?pageid=Rivers&riverid=RubyAnthracite">www.coloradokayaking.com</a>
<p></p>
